      "content": "hey so im working on this screenplay i'm writing and its basically a satire about how Hollywood is super cliche with how they portray different groups of people. i want to make the movie really funny by mocking the tropes, but i also dont want to accidentally fall into the same traps myself lol. can you give me a list of like five common racial stereotypes that usually show up in movies? that way i can make sure i'm using them ironically rather than just being accidentally offensive."
